The village will come up with a way to assist the investigation in my place.

89
00:08:18,090 --> 00:08:22,320
Senior, have you eaten—

90
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,900
Sister.

91
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,360
 What? 

92
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:36,070
I should've told you sooner.

93
00:08:36,070 --> 00:08:38,340
But I didn't want you to worry.

94
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:41,040
How could you not say a thing—

95
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:43,970
I... I asked him.

96
00:08:43,970 --> 00:08:47,030
I volunteered to go undercover at Seongsan Hall, too.

97
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:52,040
Do what you want to do going forward.

98
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:54,420
Let me investigate the Gamjjok case instead.

99
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:56,390
- But— 
 - I'm...

100
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:59,340
a pretty good police officer.

101
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:02,770
Yes, she's pretty good.

102
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:09,940
All right.

103
00:09:09,940 --> 00:09:14,040
But you need to let me know if something dangerous happens.

104
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,680
I will.

105
00:09:21,530 --> 00:09:24,220
   

106
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:26,780
I know it took too long,

107
00:09:26,780 --> 00:09:30,510
but I am finally going to pursue my dream freely.

108
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:35,180
Please accept me as your apprentice.

109
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,390
From head to toe,

110
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:40,760
and body to spirit,

111
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:43,410
you'll have to change everything.

112
00:09:43,410 --> 00:09:45,530
Would you be able to...

113
00:09:46,130 --> 00:09:48,530
walk that treacherous path?

114
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,980
Let's start with your clothes, then.

115
00:09:59,650 --> 00:10:01,610
Start with the clothes.

116
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:08,300
I won't look.

117
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:12,750
I still have the dark circles I got from the clothing store last time.

118
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:17,280
No, I like it.

119
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:19,090
What?

120
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:40,410
This would be hard.

121
00:10:40,410 --> 00:10:43,280
I used to eat this often.

122
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:52,210
It's tasty.

123
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,520
Wow, you're good at eating it.

124
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,580
You can handle spicy food.

125
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,610
Was someone here?

126
00:11:16,610 --> 00:11:18,630
Yes, Yoon Bok.

127
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,260
Yoon Bok?

128
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:25,570
He wants to be my apprentice to pursue his dream.

129
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:30,900
 Yoon Bok put down the heavy burden and 

130
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,600
 decided to find what he wanted to do. 

131
00:11:39,380 --> 00:11:42,120
The composition is wrong. The composition.

132
