I was trying to show the beauty of negative space.

133
00:11:45,570 --> 00:11:48,360
Just fill it up. Fill it up.

134
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:52,010
This is... Why did you paint the body?

135
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:55,500
Who takes a shower with clothes on?

136
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:57,790
I felt embarrassed to look at it.

137
00:11:58,470 --> 00:12:00,040
I am sorry.

138
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:03,210
You get to wash the clothes if you shower with clothes on.

139
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:06,430
You kill two birds with one stone. Don't you agree, Yoon Bok?

140
00:12:06,430 --> 00:12:08,620
I sometimes shower with clothes on.

141
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:11,660
You're supposed to be an artist, but you're so prejudiced.

142
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:14,100
How will you create good work?

143
00:12:14,740 --> 00:12:17,730
I like the negative space, too.

144
00:12:17,730 --> 00:12:21,690
Don't discourage Yoon Bok's exceptional creativity.

145
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:24,740
I'll go, then.

146
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:27,680
Have a nice day.

147
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,830
Teacher!

148
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:42,720
♫  Am I dreaming?  ♫

149
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:47,630
♫  Even after closing my eyes  ♫

150
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:54,010
♫  Even the faintest memories and nervous feeling—  ♫

151
00:12:54,010 --> 00:12:58,010
 But what changed the most is... 

